      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1761074481943,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "    Short answer: an int:\n\n    >0 = number of fds with events set (or total events),\n    0  = timeout expired,    \n    -1  = error (errno set).\n    \n    After return, inspect _pollTable[i].revents for each fd.",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "JhAUOoRyiTInE4rCN4JK8",
      "originalText": "    Short answer: an int:\n\n    >0 = number of fds with events set (or total events),\n    0  = timeout expired,    \n    -1  = error (errno set).\n    \n    After return, inspect _pollTable[i].revents for each fd.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
